---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About | Lamiae Jbira"
	description="Learn more about my background, projects and technical skills in software and web development."
>
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About Me"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Below you’ll find a quick overview of my journey and experience."
			>
				<div class = "flex justify-center gap-6">
					<img
						width="250"
						height="250"
						src="/assets/portrait.jpg"
						alt="Lamiae Jbira collaborating with a colleague"
					/>
				</div>
			</Hero>

			{/* ───────────────────────── Journey ───────────────────────── */}
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">My Journey</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						After two demanding years in preparatory classes&nbsp;(MPSI/MP) at Lycée
						d’Excellence de Benguerir, focused on mathematics and physics, I joined
						<strong> ENSEIRB-MATMECA</strong>, a top engineering school in Bordeaux. I am now
						in my final year and will graduate in&nbsp;2025 with a major in software engineering
						and backend development.
					</p>
					<p>
						Throughout my studies I have delivered multiple projects in backend, full-stack
						web and applied machine learning, sharpening both my technical skills and my
						ability to collaborate in agile teams.
					</p>
					<p>
						•&nbsp;During a four-month internship at <strong>Airbus / I2M</strong>, I built a real-time
						VR gesture-recognition pipeline (99 % accuracy, &lt; 10 ms latency).<br/>
						•&nbsp;Currently, I am interning at <strong>Atos</strong> on the <strong
					>Allianz </strong>SIDP
						platform, adding contract-lifecycle and data-integrity features with Spring Boot,
						Angular and AWS.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			{/* ───────────────────────── Education ───────────────────────── */}
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						M.Eng. in Computer Engineering (graduating 2025), ENSEIRB-MATMECA —
						specialization in software &amp; backend development.
					</p>
					<p>
						Classes préparatoires MPSI/MP (Maths & Physics), Lycée d’Excellence de Benguerir.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			{/* ───────────────────────── Skills ───────────────────────── */}
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Core Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						• <strong>Backend / Microservices:</strong> Java 17, Spring Boot 3, Node.js, REST, gRPC.<br/>
						• <strong>Web Front-End:</strong> React, TypeScript, responsive UI &amp; accessibility.<br/>
						• <strong>Data &amp; Observability:</strong> PostgreSQL, SQLite /PostGIS, Kafka,
						Jenkins, metrics &amp; logging pipelines.<br/>
						• <strong>DevOps:</strong> Docker, GitLab CI, GitHub Actions, AWS basics.<br/>
						• Passionate about clean code, TDD and continuous improvement.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
